&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/7e46c9ba-10cb-11e8-bd00-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/7e46c9ba-10cb-11e8-bd00-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_connectathon failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
